<TEXT>
a nocturnal assailant in a ski 
mask has held at least seven women at knifepoint before cutting off 
locks of their hair and fleeing 
none of the women were injured in the attacks but some were 
threatened said police the attacks all were reported in the last 
five months by women who had been walking alone at night 
the most recent episode occurred feb 17 as in previous 
attacks the woman was unable to provide an accurate description of 
the man because he wore dark clothing and a ski mask police said 
