the burbank woman was arrested jan 1 at 1130 pm for driving 
under the influence of alcohol police said her blood alcohol level 
was 12 percent a driver is considered legally drunk in california 
at 08 percent 
miss moore became an undercover informant for the fbi calling 
the mayor to a washington hotel room where he was arrested jan 18 
for investigation of possessing cocaine 
