risk was a vague term and said that removing the exemption would 
prompt unnecessary warnings and undermine consumer confidence 
robie flatly rejected that argument 
defendants interpretation that the initiative accepted 
business as usual in regulatory terms as to these important 
industries is not correct he wrote 
