delivery of diphtheria serum to nome by mail carriers driving dog 
teams in 1925 
taken overland after bad weather grounded airplanes the serum 
was credited with saving hundreds of lives in the remote town 
from downtown anchorage the course goes northwest across the 
alaska range and over the tundra before dropping down along the 
yukon river to the bering sea 
mushers must lay over for 24 hours of rest at some point along 
the trail 
