fivemember allmilitary crew of atlantis on thursday released 
into orbit a 500 million spy satellite 
the satellite is designed to take detailed pictures of the 
soviet union including areas never before viewed by 
shuttlelaunched satellites sources said it also is able to tune 
into electronic communications worldwide 
we can safely assume there are no problems as long as 
mission control does not interrupt the silence said bruce 
buckingham a spokesman for the space agency 
