i believe that its going to be a big help in this moment when 
we know the regime is falling down theyll see how the rest of 
the world is said ceferino perez of the cuban municipalities in 
exile a miami group whose members are preparing to assist their 
countrymen in rebuilding cuba in the event castro is toppled 
