put aside for recent automobileinsurance reform debate 
theres no plans to put it on the schedule immediately 
macnett said 
as to its chance for passage macnett said i wouldnt rule it 
out 
vincent carocci spokesman for gov robert p casey said the 
governor is aware of the bill but would not take a position until 
it crosses his desk 
