traded 
we germans have no territorial claims on poland we dont want 
to and will not question polands western border feldmann said 
cornelia schmalzjacobsen another leading free democrat was 
quoted as saying by the nuernberger nachrichten newspaper that the 
coalition government could be threatened by any more delays by kohl 
in openly agreeing to fixing the current border 
