think we all now know we have a major problem 
the next election is not due until 1991 or 1992 and mrs 
thatcher has time to quiet the controversy by pouring in government 
money to cushion the hardest hit districts 
so far she has adamantly insisted that the community charge is a 
fairer system and will not be changed 
