<TEXT>
the 1990 audi v8 quattro is as close to a swagger as the folks 
at audi get 
this 47450 power machine is quietly packaged in decidedly audi 
styling the luxury eurosedan look thats relatively unassuming 
but take this new flagship of the audi fleet out on the highway 
